task.summary: Add thread context for tracking objects
Added BoneCP for managing database connection pool for each thread
Deleted unnecessary files. Performed basic code refactor
Fixed bug where each thread gets its own JDBC pool (made it shared)
Added financialqueryrestservice for posting cost objects for a given user. Added Jackson dependency

Can now query DB for CostObject, deserialize it into CostObjectDTO, serialize it back into JSON format, and pass it the the UI. The necessary RestAPIs are surfaced for the UI to perform the CostObject query.
